'''四氯化铌'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为NbCl<sub>4</sub>。它是暗紫色晶体，对空气和湿气十分敏感，受热（400℃）歧化为[[三氯化铌|三氯化铌]]和[[五氯化铌|五氯化铌]]。<ref name = Macintyre>Macintyre, J.E.; Daniel, F.M.; Chapman and Hall; Stirling, V.M.  Dictionary of Inorganic Compounds.  1992, Cleveland, OH: CRC Press, p. 2957</ref>

==制备==
四氯化铌通常由[[铌|铌]]和[[五氯化铌|五氯化铌]]晶体升温反应得到，金属在400°C，五氯化铌在250°C：<ref name = McCarley>{{cite journal |author1=McCarley, Robert E. |author2=Torp, Bruce A. | title = The preparation and properties of niobium(IV) compounds. I. Some niobium(IV) halides and their pyridine adducts | journal = [[Inorg._Chem.|Inorg. Chem.]] | doi = 10.1021/ic50007a029 | year = 1963 | volume = 2 | pages = 540 | issue = 3}}</ref>
:4 NbCl<sub>5</sub> + Nb → 5 NbCl<sub>4</sub>
用金属[[铝|铝]]还原五氯化铌也能得到产物：
:3 NbCl<sub>5</sub> + Al → 3 NbCl<sub>4</sub> + AlCl<sub>3</sub>

